title: Real Humans S1 Ep1
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep1

Break In, Break Loose - This ten-part Swedish drama series is set in a parallel present day in which robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. This new generation of 'hubots' were initially created to be mechanised servants and labourers. However, as an ever growing number of people begin to form intimate relationships with hubots, the boundaries between human and machine become blurred. Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
